1.0.3

* added scoring
* cleaned todo list

1.0.4

* Support smaller terminals (as small as 19x19)
* Support terminal resize
* Support B&W terminals
* Support command line options
* Workaround nasty ALTLinux/Debian GPM bug
* Persist high scores
* Added man page
